  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_99712110-222C-0135-DC0C-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To edit the settings of an existing quiz, locate the quiz [1]. Classic Quizzes display an empty Quiz icon [2]. New Quizzes display a filled quiz icon [3]. </p>
<p>To edit the quiz, click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [4], and select the <strong>Edit</strong> option [5]. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
