  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_997214A0-222C-0135-DC12-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To set an Available From date, click the calendar icon [1] and select the date [2] and time [3]. Click the <strong>Done</strong> button [4].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

